  "title": "Peppery Silky Canadian Chicken Stir-fry",
  "description": "A monsoon-inspired dish featuring poached chicken thighs with a touch of peppery flavors and silky texture, suitable for pescatarian diets.",
  "cuisine": "Canadian",
