  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oil in a pan over medium heat. Season chicken thighs with salt and pepper.",
    "Sear chicken on all sides until golden brown, about 3 minutes per side.",
    "Add garlic, tomato paste, chili garlic paste, and shallots to the pan. Stir-fry for another minute.",
    "Pour water into the pan, bring to a boil, then reduce heat to simmer.",
    "Simmer for 10-15 minutes until chicken is cooked through. Add pepper flakes during the last 2-3 minutes of cooking.",
    "Remove from heat and let cool slightly before slicing or serving."
  ],
